EKSEMPEL OF USE: REMEMBER RUN WITH DEV

### Get all trips
GET {{url}}/trips
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

### Get trip by ID
GET {{url}}/trips/1
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

### Create new trip
POST {{url}}/trips
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

{
  "name": "Winter Escape",
  "startTime": "2025-12-15T00:00:00",
  "endTime": "2025-12-22T00:00:00",
  "latitude": 46.5,
  "longitude": 9.8,
  "price": 2800,
  "category": "SNOW"
}

### Update trip
PUT {{url}}/trips/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

{
  "name": "Updated Winter Escape",
  "startTime": "2025-12-15T00:00:00",
  "endTime": "2025-12-22T00:00:00",
  "latitude": 46.5,
  "longitude": 9.8,
  "price": 3000,
  "category": "SNOW"
}

### Delete trip
DELETE {{url}}/trips/1
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

### Assign guide to trip
PUT {{url}}/trips/1/guides/2
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

### Get total trip value per guide
GET {{url}}/trips/guides/totalprice
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

### Get packing weight for trip (external API)
GET {{url}}/trips/1/packing/weight
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}
